Opie & Jim Norton OCT 30 2015 Fri (03:01:13)


On Today's Show:

JIM FLORENTINE, MARK NORMAND, DAN RATHER, AARON KRAUSE, WILL FORTE. 
 
Addiction talk, Justin's power outage, college Halloween consultants, Judy Gold makes the headlines, The best worst sexy halloween costumes of 2015, Jim Florentine calls in & talks Halloween & Sports. Mark Normand joins the boys in studio then is asked if anything happened with Kaitlyn Farrington after yesterday's show. Dan Rather in studio to talk about the movie 'TRUTH', career stories & more. Jared Fogle audio with Uncle Paul commentry. Aaron Krause inventor of 'Scrub Daddy' in studio to talk about the process of coming up with a new product & more. Will Forte in studio. A few things will talks about are being a writer for late night shows, Snl stories & more
